<subSubSection id="C37F6542FF84ED502BC9F8C3FAACF873" pageId="18" pageNumber="19" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8BDA36C9FF84ED502BC9F8C3FAACF873" blockId="18.[151,1436,1832,2022]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">
<emphasis id="B911EADBFF84ED502BC9F8C3FEFEF807" bold="true" box="[198,326,1912,1938]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Wing hyaline with brownish antero-distal macula; R 
<number id="3DAD24EEFF84ED5028B9F832FC06F802" box="[950,958,1929,1943]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19" value="2.0">2</number>
+ 
<number id="3DAD24EEFF84ED5028C7F832FC77F802" box="[968,975,1929,1943]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19" value="3.0">3</number>
reaching C far from R 
<number id="3DAD24EEFF84ED502FD3F832FB5CF802" box="[1244,1252,1929,1943]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19" value="1.0">1</number>
, with wide distal concavity; areas around crossveins r-m and m-m pigmented; pterostigma rounded, large; meso-anterior incision of tergite IX on male rather short; many golden setae on scutum, scutellum and abdomen.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
